  "text": "Many factors determine the choice of treatment of odontoid fractures. There is no current consensus on a preference between anterior or posterior surgical approach [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . The most appropriate approach should be selected based on the individual characteristics of the patient and the fracture.",
